  "body": "### Description\n\nAs of now, the only way to ask for dev services to be run in the shared network is to produce a `DevServicesSharedNetworkBuildItem`, which I think is only done here : https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/blob/607ece496231d6278471e76c337d8637bc67c640/test-framework/junit5/src/main/java/io/quarkus/test/junit/IntegrationTestUtil.java#L292.\r\n\r\nIt would be great to be able to ask for it through configuration. I first thought that was what quarkus.<extension>.devservice.shared was for, it turned out it was not ;).\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
